<h2 id="bio">Bio</h2>
<p>Charles is a graduate research assistant at North Carolina State University Department of Nuclear Engineering working towards his MS and PhD in nuclear engineering.</p>

<h2 id="research">Research</h2>
<p>He is conducting research under Dr. Anistratov exploring hybrid deterministic-stochastic methods for neutron transport problems. Interests include scientific computing, numerical analysis, and acceleration techniques.</p>
